================================

**Cancelled: Government Tender Announcement - NRCan**

**Reference Number:** PW-22-01015573
**Solicitation Number:** NRCan - 5000071455

**Publication Date:** December 1, 2022
**Tender Closing Date:** December 15, 2022 (2:00 PM ET)
**Notice Type:** Request for Proposal (Demande de propositions)

**Contracting Entity:**
Natural Resources Canada (Ressources naturelles Canada)
580 Booth Street, Ottawa, Ontario K1A 0E4, Canada

**Description:**
This tender announcement has been cancelled by the contracting entity. The original request for proposal has been withdrawn from the market.

**Trade Agreements:**
This procurement is governed by the following trade agreements:
- Canadian Free Trade Agreement (Accord de libre-échange canadien)
- Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (Accord de libre-échange Canada-Corée)

**Regions:**
This tender is open to Canadian companies. However, the contract will be delivered in **Ontario (except for the National Capital Region)**.

**Critical Fields:**
No selection criteria have been designated. As a result, the procurement method is open to all registered and eligible Canadian firms.

**Point of Contact:**

Julia Pace
Natural Resources Canada
1 Challenger Drive, Dartmouth, NS B2Y 4A2, Canada
Phone: 902-719-4856
Email: [julia.pace@nrcan-rncan.gc.ca](mailto:julia.pace@nrcan-rncan.gc.ca)
